platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Quick look at your screen time

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: An advanced screen-time tracker, with focus timers, boundary setting tools and in-depth screen-time statistics. Understand your digital habits, set goals and learn how to focus better on the things that matter to you.

OffScreen is more than a screen-time tracker. With focus timers and in-depth screen-time statistics, OffScreen helps you understand your digital habits and gives you the tools to set boundariesand see your goals through. By tracking everything from how many times you pick up your phone to how often you use it while walking, youll learn how to focus better on the things that matter to you.

Un outil avanc de suivi du temps dcran, avec des minuteurs de concentration, des limites et des statistiques exhaustives. Analysez vos habitudes, fixez-vous des objectifs et apprenez  mieux vous concentrer sur lessentiel.
